description: Get detailed data for the service sync blocker summary.

parameters.name: serviceName
parameters.description: The name of the service that you want to get the service sync blocker summary for. If given only the service name, all instances are blocked.

nested_items.name: serviceSyncBlockerSummary
nested_items.description: The detailed data of the requested service sync blocker summary.

nested_items.name: latestBlockers
nested_items.description: The latest active blockers for the synced service.

nested_items.name: contexts
nested_items.description: The contexts for the sync blocker.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: The key for the sync blocker context.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The value of the sync blocker context.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time when the sync blocker was created.

nested_items.name: createdReason
nested_items.description: The reason why the sync blocker was created.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the sync blocker.

nested_items.name: resolvedAt
nested_items.description: The time the sync blocker was resolved.

nested_items.name: resolvedReason
nested_items.description: The reason the sync blocker was resolved.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the sync blocker.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The type of the sync blocker.

nested_items.name: serviceInstanceName
nested_items.description: The name of the service instance that you want sync your service configuration with.

nested_items.name: serviceName
nested_items.description: The name of the service that you want to get the sync blocker summary for. If given a service instance name and a service name, it will return the blockers only applying to the instance that is blocked.
